summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 6274 for the improvement of 34th Ave. Southwest from Southwest Kenyon St. to Southwest Roxbury St.; and certain other streets and avenues; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 91733, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
